On Stampede2, the CPUs on login node and job nodes are different. If we use "-xHost", we will have the "illegal instruction" error. 
To avoid these CPU instructions, we manually set the FCFLAGS and CCFLAGS. Following is for KNL nodes.

./configure FC=ifort CC=icc --with-dft-flavor='libxc+bigdft' ./configure FC=ifort CC=icc  FCFLAGS="-xMIC-AVX512  -O2  -g -extend-source -vec-report0 -noaltparam -nofpscomp"  CCFLAGS="-xMIC-AVX512  -O2 -g -extend-source -vec-report0 -noaltparam -nofpscomp"
